# Large query-embedding parquets are stored via Git LFS.
#
# Scope: all embedding parquets under benchmark/cache/emb/. These are the only
# LFS-worthy files in the repo (~20-50 MB each); every other tracked file is <2 MB.
#
# NOTE: the headline `gemini__*` embeddings were committed as regular git blobs in
# the initial release and are intentionally NOT migrated into LFS — that would
# rewrite published history. The rule below therefore takes effect for newly added
# embedders (e.g. qwen8b) and any future re-add of the gemini files.
benchmark/cache/emb/*.parquet filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
